However, the crystallinity of the film formed by electrospinning was significantly lower than that of the film formed by casting, and the film formed by coaxial electrospinning had the lowest crystallinity. Moreover, that of the film with DAS added was significantly lower than that of the film without DAS under the same conditions, indicating that the addition of DAS may reduce the crystallinity of the gelatin-chitosan film.
